            "html": "<p class=\"q-text qu-display--block\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1em; overflow-wrap: anywhere; word-break: break-word; direction: ltr; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">A2A</span></p> <p class=\"q-text qu-display--block\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1em; overflow-wrap: anywhere; word-break: break-word; direction: ltr; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">It's up to you if you want to hire a personal trainer, but that's not needed.<br>I would say the best site to follow would be </span><span class=\"q-inline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline;\"><a class=\"q-box qu-cursor--pointer qu-hover--textDecoration--underline Link___StyledBox-t2xg9c-0 roKEj\" title=\"bodybuilding.com\" href=\"http://bodybuilding.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; border-radius: inherit; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">http://bodybuilding.com</a><span class=\"q-inlineBlock qu-verticalAlign--text-bottom\" width=\"16px\" name=\"ExternalLink\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 0; margin-left: 2px;\"><span class=\"CssComponent__CssInlineComponent-sc-1oskqb9-1 Icon___StyledCssInlineComponent-sc-11tmcw7-0 bxnMMA\"><svg width=\"24px\" height=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g id=\"external_link\" class=\"icon_svg-stroke\" stroke=\"#666\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"17 13.5 17 19.5 5 19.5 5 7.5 11 7.5\"></polyline><path d=\"M14,4.5 L20,4.5 L20,10.5 M20,4.5 L11,13.5\"></path></g></svg></span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\"><br>That's the the only site i follow really closely, elliot hulse is also a great guy to follow on you tube as I feel he gives really great advice. apart from these too I hardly follow any other ones. </span></p> <p class=\"q-text qu-display--block\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1em; overflow-wrap: anywhere; word-break: break-word; direction: ltr; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">I feel that it's the simplest and best site out there is. As far as starting out is concerned just try one one of the beginner programs you can find there and stick to it for the duration of that program. Do not give up in the middle saying you are not getting the kind of results you want. Some times you might not get the results even at the end of that program as most of those programs are maybe 2-4 months. </span></p> <p class=\"q-text qu-display--block\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1em; overflow-wrap: anywhere; word-break: break-word; direction: ltr; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\"><br>The main thing you will learn at the end of the program is though sticking to a diet, some basics about lifting and importance of form among various exercises.</span></p> <p class=\"q-text qu-display--block\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1em; overflow-wrap: anywhere; word-break: break-word; direction: ltr; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">I personally started out with kris gethin 12 week trainer as it had videos for every single workout day and it helped me with my form initially. Initially i didn't know much about diet and followed the exact same thing he suggested but reduced portions compared to what was published over there as I weighed less. </span></p> <p class=\"q-text qu-display--block\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1em; overflow-wrap: anywhere; word-break: break-word; direction: ltr; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">While I was doing the workouts I was constantly researching on the side about nutrition and different exercises and how I was responding to those different exercises in different ways and how some of the popular exercises might not be good for you because of your body type. It took almost a year and finally now I feel like I am at a level where I can design a program for myself and change it up according to my needs. </span></p> <p class=\"q-text qu-display--block\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1em; overflow-wrap: anywhere; word-break: break-word; direction: ltr; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">There is no secret program to getting the best results or the perfect diet. It all depends on your body and you have to try a lot of things to find out your ideal requirements.</span></p> <p class=\"q-text qu-display--block\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px; overflow-wrap: anywhere; word-break: break-word; direction: ltr; text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">A final article I recommend to read. It makes some great points and some useful tips to create a diet. You could use this as a base for planning your diet.<br></span><span class=\"q-inline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline;\"><a class=\"q-box qu-cursor--pointer qu-hover--textDecoration--underline Link___StyledBox-t2xg9c-0 roKEj\" title=\"www.simplyshredded.com\" href=\"http://www.simplyshredded.com/layne-norton-the-most-effective-cutting-diet.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; border-radius: inherit; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; background: none;\">The Ultimate Cutting Diet - Devised By Pro Natural Bodybuilder Layne Norton</a><span class=\"q-inlineBlock qu-verticalAlign--text-bottom\" width=\"16px\" name=\"ExternalLink\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; width: 16px; height: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 0; margin-left: 2px;\"><span class=\"CssComponent__CssInlineComponent-sc-1oskqb9-1 Icon___StyledCssInlineComponent-sc-11tmcw7-0 bxnMMA\"><svg width=\"24px\" height=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><g id=\"external_link\" class=\"icon_svg-stroke\" stroke=\"#666\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><polyline points=\"17 13.5 17 19.5 5 19.5 5 7.5 11 7.5\"></polyline><path d=\"M14,4.5 L20,4.5 L20,10.5 M20,4.5 L11,13.5\"></path></g></svg></span></span></span></p>",
